  "detailed_description": "<h1>Workshop Description</h1><p>Some players don't know how to open the creative workshop, This picture is the order to open the creative workshop, I wish you a happy game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/144d5079b691949b2279af03edc2f54f.avif?t=1766505381\" width=510 height=286 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>\"Picture toys\" is an improved version of the traditional puzzle game, Added touch and graffiti features, Also supports creative workshops, Upload and download content from creative workshops, Can share pictures with each other !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/7965e65fbedcea52096565d75aec15ba.avif?t=1766505381\" width=510 height=184 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Jelly effect</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/e3bab7cba06a4cf26ac2dffdbbe9c5b8.poster.avif?t=1766505381\" width=510 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/e3bab7cba06a4cf26ac2dffdbbe9c5b8.webm?t=1766505381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/e3bab7cba06a4cf26ac2dffdbbe9c5b8.mp4?t=1766505381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Graffiti function</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/05b9a4c56fc991877d3988084878e300.poster.avif?t=1766505381\" width=510 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/05b9a4c56fc991877d3988084878e300.webm?t=1766505381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181120/extras/05b9a4c56fc991877d3988084878e300.mp4?t=1766505381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support creative workshop, Can share pictures with each other</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 100 creative workshop items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traditional jigsaw puzzle</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Can import images, support jpg, png format</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>F key to complete the puzzle quickly</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Right mouse button automatic touch</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Touch range R, touch intensity S, touch elasticity E can be adjusted</li></ul>",
